lookin' after 'em at night.

9
00:04:58,111 --> 00:05:01,808
Now, what I want
is a camp tender...

10
00:05:02,882 --> 00:05:06,181
to stay in
the main camp, where
the Forest Service says.

11
00:05:06,253 --> 00:05:07,880
But the herder...

12
