23
00:05:43,088 --> 00:05:46,888
You got your dogs,
your .30-30, you sleep there.

24
00:05:47,493 --> 00:05:51,554
Last summer I had
goddamn near 25% loss.
I don't want that again.

25
00:05:52,097 --> 00:05:53,155
You.

26
00:05:54,700 --> 00:05:57,430
Fridays at noon,
be down at the bridge...

27
00:05:57,836 --> 00:06:00,236
with your grocery list
and mules...

28
00:06:00,306 --> 00:06:04,003
and somebody with supplies
will be there at the pick-up.

29
00:06:06,645 --> 00:06:09,944
Tomorrow mornin' we'll
truck you up to the jump-off.

30
00:06:38,377 --> 00:06:40,971
Jack Twist.
Ennis.

31
00:06:42,414 --> 00:06:45,679
Your folks
just stop at Ennis?
Del Mar.

32
00:06:47,353 --> 00:06:49,616
Well, nice to know you,
Ennis Del Mar.

33
00:07:08,039 --> 00:07:09,939
My second year up here.

34
00:07:11,175 --> 00:07:14,474
Last year, one storm,
the lightnin'
killed 42 sheep.

35
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:18,274
Thought I'd asphyxiate
from the smell.

36
00:07:18,683 --> 00:07:23,086
Aguirre got all over my ass,
like I was supposed to
control the weather.

37
00:07:23,254 --> 00:07:27,384
But beats workin' for
my old man. Can't please
my old man, no way.

38
00:07:29,093 --> 00:07:32,756
That's why I took
to rodeoin'. You ever rodeo?

39
00:07:34,298 --> 00:07:37,199
You know, I mean,
once in a while.

40
00:07:37,935 --> 00:07:40,460
When I got the entry fee
in my pocket.

41
00:07:40,538 --> 00:07:41,630
Yeah.

42
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:45,065
Are you from ranch people?

43
00:07:45,209 --> 00:07:46,608
Yeah, I was.

44
00:07:48,346 --> 00:07:50,246
Your folks run you off?

45
00:07:51,416 --> 00:07:54,214
No, they run themselves off.
There was...

46
00:07:55,620 --> 00:07:58,952
one curve in the road in
43 miles, and they miss it.

47
00:08:00,624 --> 00:08:03,422
So the bank took the ranch...

48
00:08:03,493 --> 00:08:06,587
and my brother and sister,
they raised me, mostly.

49
00:08:09,399 --> 00:08:11,594
Shit, that's hard.

50
