are hard to pack.

55
00:08:48,705 --> 00:08:50,605
Well, I don't eat soup.

56
00:08:55,879 --> 00:08:59,576
You wanna watch it there.
That horse has
a low startle point.

57
00:09:00,116 --> 00:09:02,812
Doubt there's a filly
that could throw me.

58
00:09:03,453 --> 00:09:07,149
