and I won't have
to put up with
Joe Aguirre's crap no more.

62
00:11:57,391 --> 00:11:59,621
I'm savin' for
a place myself.

63
00:12:01,762 --> 00:12:06,028
Alma and me, we're gonna
get married when I come
down off this mountain.

64
00:12:06,133 --> 00:12:09,296
