that stay with the sheep,
no fire bullshit.

65
00:12:10,771 --> 00:12:14,605
Aguirre got no right
makin' us do somethin'
against the rules.

66
00:13:03,956 --> 00:13:05,446
No more beans.

67
00:13:39,525 --> 00:13:41,720
Damn. Shit!

68
00:13:45,597 --> 00:13:47,724
