Something wrong?

69
00:13:49,033 --> 00:13:50,227
Yeah, so what...

70
00:13:50,301 --> 00:13:52,929
Why didn't we get
the powdered milk
and the spuds?

71
00:13:53,004 --> 00:13:54,494
That's all we got.

72
00:13:55,106 --> 00:13:56,334
Well...

73
00:13:57,175 --> 00:13:58,870
Here's next week's.

74
00:14:01,379 --> 00:14:04,837
Thought you didn't eat soup.
Yeah, well,
I'm sick of beans.

75
00:14:04,916 --> 00:14:07,817
Too early in the summer
to be sick of beans.

76
00:14:10,588 --> 00:14:11,816
Come on.

77
00:14:34,712 --> 00:14:36,270
Come on. Come on.

78
00:14:47,659 --> 00:14:49,286
Hold on. Whoa, whoa!

79
00:14:52,931 --> 00:14:53,919
Shit.

80
00:14:55,032 --> 00:14:57,023
Whoa. Come back here!

81
00:15:35,505 --> 00:15:37,029
Whoa there, whoa.

82
00:15:37,174 --> 00:15:38,937
All right. Fuck it.

83
00:15:40,410 --> 00:15:42,310
Okay, you bastard.

84
00:15:45,649 --> 00:15:47,082
Where the hell you been?

85
00:15:47,150 --> 00:15:49,641
