everywhere.

91
00:16:06,035 --> 00:16:09,801
Beans is about
all we got left.
Got whiskey or somethin'?

92
00:16:15,311 --> 00:16:16,801
Dumb-ass mule.

93
00:16:21,717 --> 00:16:24,948
I can't believe that.
God damn.

94
00:16:26,555 --> 00:16:28,147
Let me see.

95
00:16:34,130 --> 00:16:35,222
Shit.

96
00:16:35,765 --> 00:16:39,223
Well, we gotta do somethin'
about this food situation.

97
00:16:39,669 --> 00:16:42,103
Maybe I'll shoot
one of the sheep.

98
00:16:42,405 --> 00:16:44,839
Yeah, what if
Aguirre finds out, huh?

99
00:16:44,907 --> 00:16:46,875
We're supposed to guard
the sheep, not eat 'em.

100
00:16:46,943 --> 00:16:50,401
What's the matter with you?
There are a thousand of 'em.

101
00:16:51,547 --> 00:16:53,412
I'll stick with beans.

102
00:16:55,718 --> 00:16:57,208
Well, I won't.

103
00:17:11,100 --> 00:17:12,124
Yeah!

104
00:17:12,201 --> 00:17:14,828
Gettin' tired
of your dumb-ass missin'.

105
00:17:15,070 --> 00:17:16,503
Let's get a move on.

106
00:17:16,571 --> 00:17:19,540
Don't want the Game and Fish
to catch us with no elk.

107
00:17:44,366 --> 00:17:46,527
Come on. Shit.

108
00:17:53,575 --> 00:17:56,100
Yeah, I'm commutin'
four hours a day.

109
00:17:56,945 --> 00:18:00,039
I come in for breakfast,
I go back to the sheep.

110
00:18:00,415 --> 00:18:02,542
Evenin',
get 'em bedded down.

111
00:18:02,617 --> 00:18:05,381
Come in for supper,
go back to the sheep.

112
00:18:06,421 --> 00:18:09,481
Spend half the night
checkin' for damn coyotes.

113
00:18:10,291 --> 00:18:12,919
Aguirre got no right
to make me do this.

114
00:18:15,730 --> 00:18:18,028
You wanna switch?
I wouldn't mind
sleepin' out there.

115
00:18:18,099 --> 00:18:21,933
That ain't the point.
The point is, we both
ought to be in this camp.

116
00:18:22,736 --> 00:18:25,864
Goddamn pup tent smells
like cat piss or worse.

117
00:18:26,640 --> 00:18:28,972
I wouldn't mind
bein' out there.

118
00:18:32,312 --> 00:18:34,644
Well, I'm happy
to switch with you...

119
00:18:34,715 --> 00:18:37,309
but I warn you,
I can't cook worth a damn.

120
00:18:37,918 --> 00:18:40,751
I am pretty good
with a can opener, though.

121
00:18:41,655 --> 00:18:44,146
You can't be no worse
than me, then.

122
00:18:45,025 --> 00:18:46,424
Here you go.

123
00:18:56,503 --> 00:18:58,869
You won't get much sleep,
I'll tell you that.

124
00:18:58,939 --> 00:19:00,668
Yup. Come on.

125
00:19:20,394 --> 00:19:22,362
Shot a coyote up there.

126
00:19:23,297 --> 00:19:26,994
It's a big son of a bitch.
He had balls on him
the size of apples.

127
00:19:27,968 --> 00:19:30,835
He looked like
he could eat himself a camel.

128
00:19:32,338 --> 00:19:34,636
You want
some of this hot water?

129
00:19:38,344 --> 00:19:39,868
It's all yours.

130
00:20:06,239 --> 00:20:07,331
Mmm.

131
00:20:19,051 --> 00:20:21,042
I don't rodeo much myself.

132
00:20:21,821 --> 00:20:22,981
I mean,
what's the point...

133
00:20:23,055 --> 00:20:25,717
