It's too late to go
to them sheep.

193
00:25:28,622 --> 00:25:30,613
Well, you got
an extra blanket?

194
00:25:30,758 --> 00:25:34,592
I'll just roll up out here,
grab 40 winks...

195
00:25:34,995 --> 00:25:37,395
and I'll ride out
at first light.

196
00:25:41,435 --> 00:25:44,131
You'll freeze your ass off
when that fire dies down.

197
00:25:44,205 --> 00:25:45,502
Oh, that's good.

198
00:25:45,573 --> 00:25:47,541
You're better off
sleepin' in the tent.

199
00:25:47,608 --> 00:25:48,700
Yeah.

200
00:25:50,377 --> 00:25:51,708
All right.

201
00:26:28,115 --> 00:26:30,446
Ennis!
What?

202
00:26:31,084 --> 00:26:33,814
Just quit your yammerin'
and get in here!

203
00:27:35,148 --> 00:27:37,275
Come on, come on.

204
00:27:46,525 --> 00:27:48,254
What are you doin'?

205
00:29:55,252 --> 00:29:56,980
See you for supper.

206
00:29:58,388 --> 00:29:59,878
Yeah. Come on.

207
00:30:37,927 --> 00:30:39,189
Come on.

208
00:32:04,079 --> 00:32:06,912
This is a one-shot thing
we got goin' on here.

209
00:32:12,287 --> 00:32:14,585
